---
import ProductPageLayout from '../../layouts/ProductPageLayout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<ProductPageLayout
  title="GenAI Firewall — AI Shield"
  description="Inspect and protect every GenAI prompt and response. Prevent sensitive data leakage to ChatGPT, Copilot, and enterprise AI tools."
  heroHeading="GenAI Firewall"
  heroSubheading="Inspect, classify, and protect every prompt and response across your enterprise GenAI tools — in real time."
>
  <!-- Stat Callout -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
      <p class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white mb-4">
        75<span class="text-accent-primary">%</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        of employees use GenAI tools at work. Every prompt is a potential data leak — customer PII, source code, financial projections, and trade secrets flowing to third-party models.
      </p>
      <p class="text-accent-primary font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mt-4">What are they sharing?</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Capabilities -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <SectionHeading tag="Capabilities" title="Six layers of GenAI protection" align="left" />

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <!-- Capability 1: Prompt Inspection -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2">Prompt Inspection</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-3">
          Every prompt and response is scanned in real time before it reaches the AI provider. AI Shield identifies sensitive data including PII, PHI, PCI data, source code, credentials, API keys, and proprietary business information.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Sub-50ms latency — users never notice the inspection</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>NLP-based detection catches context-dependent sensitive data</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Inspects both prompts (outbound) and responses (inbound)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 2: Protection Actions -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2">Protection Actions</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-3">
          When sensitive data is detected, AI Shield takes configurable action — block the prompt, redact the sensitive portion, replace with synthetic data, or allow with logging. Policies are granular per data type, user role, and AI tool.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Block, redact, replace, or allow-and-log modes</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>User receives inline explanation of why a prompt was modified</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Smart replacement preserves prompt intent while removing sensitive data</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 3: AI Coverage -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2">AI Tool Coverage</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-3">
          Protect every GenAI touchpoint in your enterprise. AI Shield supports browser-based tools, API integrations, IDE extensions, and custom enterprise AI applications.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Copilot, and 50+ GenAI tools</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>API proxy for custom LLM integrations (OpenAI, Azure OpenAI, Bedrock)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Browser extension for web-based GenAI tools</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 4: Policy Control -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2">Policy Control</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-3">
          Define granular policies that match your organization's risk tolerance. Set rules by department, role, data type, AI tool, and regulatory context. No one-size-fits-all — every team gets the right balance of productivity and protection.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Department-level policies (engineering: allow code, block PII; legal: block everything)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Pre-built policy templates for HIPAA, GDPR, PCI-DSS, SOX</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Policy simulation mode — test rules before enforcement</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 5: Visibility & Analytics -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2">Visibility & Analytics</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-3">
          See exactly how your organization uses GenAI — which tools, which departments, what data types are being shared, and where the highest risk lies. Real-time dashboards give security teams the visibility they need.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Real-time dashboard with GenAI usage trends and risk scoring</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Drill-down by department, tool, user, and sensitive data category</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Weekly executive reports with risk summaries and trend analysis</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 6: SIEM Integration -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2">SIEM Integration</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-3">
          Every GenAI interaction generates an audit event that flows into your existing security infrastructure. Correlate GenAI data exposure events with your broader security posture.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Native integration with Splunk, Microsoft Sentinel, IBM QRadar, Elastic</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>CEF and LEEF log format support for any SIEM platform</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-text-secondary-dark">
            <span class="text-accent-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
            <span>Pre-built correlation rules for DLP and insider threat workflows</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pipeline Context -->
  <section class="mb-8">
    <SectionHeading tag="Better Together" title="Part of the AI Shield pipeline" align="left" />

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-text-secondary-dark">
        The GenAI Firewall is one layer of AI Shield's end-to-end data compliance platform. While the firewall protects data at the point of GenAI interaction, the full pipeline ensures that the data feeding your AI systems was protected from the start.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div>
            <p class="font-mono text-accent-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Upstream</p>
            <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-2">Training Data Protection</h4>
            <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm">
              Before data enters your ML pipelines, AI Shield discovers, classifies, and de-identifies sensitive records. Models are trained on compliant data from day one.
            </p>
            <a href="/platform/training-data" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-accent-primary text-sm font-semibold mt-3 hover:underline">
              Learn more
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-mono text-accent-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Real-time</p>
            <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-2">GenAI Firewall</h4>
            <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm">
              At the point of interaction, the firewall inspects every prompt and response to prevent sensitive data from leaking to GenAI providers.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-accent-secondary text-sm font-semibold mt-3">
              You are here
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-mono text-accent-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Governance</p>
            <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-2">Provenance & Audit</h4>
            <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm">
              Every action across the pipeline is documented with tamper-proof certificates. When regulators ask questions, you have answers.
            </p>
            <a href="/platform" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-accent-primary text-sm font-semibold mt-3 hover:underline">
              See full pipeline
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-bg-secondary/50 rounded-xl border border-accent-primary/20 p-6">
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-2">Why both layers matter</h4>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-4">
          Protecting training data ensures your models do not memorize sensitive information. The GenAI Firewall ensures your employees do not feed sensitive information into external models. Together, they close the two largest AI data risk vectors in the enterprise.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-danger mt-0.5 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-medium">Without AI Shield</p>
              <p class="text-text-secondary-dark">Sensitive data leaks in two directions — into models during training and out through GenAI prompts. No visibility into either.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-medium">With AI Shield</p>
              <p class="text-text-secondary-dark">Training data is de-identified before model training. GenAI prompts are inspected in real time. Full audit trail for both.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ProductPageLayout>
